South Africa Daybook: Interest Rates on Hold, Crop Estimates, Bond Auction

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-24T06:05:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-24/south-africa-daybook-interest-rates-on-hold-crop-estimates-bond-auction.html
South Africa  will keep its
benchmark interest rate unchanged at a 30-year low of 5.5
percent, according to all 23 economists surveyed by Bloomberg.  Reserve Bank Governor  Gill Marcus  will announce the
decision from about 3 p.m. in  Pretoria .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at   vwessels@bloomberg.net  